# Finance Dashboard — project context

Behavioral rules: [golden-rule.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/golden-rule.mdc). Agent index: [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md). Deep docs: `docs/` (on-demand, not duplicated here).

## Layout

- `backend/` — Express + Prisma + SQLite (`prisma/schema.prisma`, `src/app.ts`, `src/fx.ts`, `src/auth.ts`)
- `frontend/` — Vite + React + TypeScript (`src/components/`, `src/api/`, `src/state/`)
- Repository root: `npm run dev`, `npm run build`

## Local dev

- Root: `npm run dev` (backend `:4000`, frontend `:5173`). Setup, env, seed: [README.md](mdc:README.md).

## Conventions

- **LF only** — [line-endings.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/line-endings.mdc), `.editorconfig`, `.gitattributes`.
- Minimal diff (golden-rule). New routes in `backend/src/app.ts`; API clients in `frontend/src/api/`; UI in `frontend/src/components/`.
- Schema changes: `cd backend && npx prisma migrate dev --name <description>` — see [README.md](mdc:README.md) for reset notes.
